title: Ebro In The Morning - JB Smoove + The Artist Formerly Known As Kanye
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/19.

The crew discusses the death of Colin Powell (1) and the feud between AEW and WWE. (50) Actor and Comedian - JB Smoove joins the program to talk Chappelle and Curb Your Enthusiasm. (31)
